NodeMon - ek package hai jo automatic file ko run karta hai save hone par
syntax= nodemon index or npm start
Third modules = installed via NPM
local modules = developers create karta hai
here we used require keyword to call modules while in react we used import 
module.exports= name jisko export karna hai ==> now u can use this module anywhere  , it is default expoert
if u want to do more than 2 things export then u cant use default export u have to use named export
named expoert=> module.exports={ name of all which u want to export} 

Express Js = it is a lightweight and flexible node.js web application framework
usign this = u can use MVC package model view controller
if project bohot bada= use express
express js simplifies=
1. routing - http ka use karke karta hai , methods=Get,Post,Put,delete ,etc supports dynamic and nested routes
2. middleware = main route or functionality k bich mai kaam karta hai
3. RestFul API support
